long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
【 How to use 】
1. Ship For Me - You can submit the tracking information directly to moomol.com by clicking “Add Parcel” on the Taobao/Tmall page where the product has bought. In addition, you can also edit the added package.
2. Buy For Me - You can add items directly to the Moomol shopping cart by clicking on "Buy For Me" on the Taobao/Tmall product page.
3. Browse the website - Click the Moomol icon on the right side of the browser and a small window will appear to display the moomol.com website.

【 Our service 】
Moomol Provide simple, reasonable, safe and fast shipping on Sea,  Air and Express services, China to Malaysia.

Thank you very much for using Moomol Chrome app.
With your support, we will continue to do it better.
